Package com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest

The com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest package provides interfaces for dealing with the guest operating system.

Package com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest Description

The com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest package provides interfaces for dealing with the guest operating system. This includes information about the state of local file systems and network interfaces and methods to manipulate the guest file system and processes.
